Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: IF EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Aplications WHERE Token = @IToken) SET @OVal = 1 ELSE SET @OVal = 0 RETURN 0

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT ParameterId, Code, ISNULL(Description,'') AS Description, ISNULL(Valor1,'') AS Valor1, ISNULL(Valor2,'') AS Valor2 FROM Parameters WHERE Status = 1 AND (Code = @ICode OR @ICode = '') AND (Description = @IDescription OR @IDescription='')

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: UPDATE Profiles SET Status = 0 WHERE ProfileId = @IProfileId

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value:
INSERT INTO Profiles ( Description, Status ) VALUES ( @IDescription, 1 )
SET @OProfileId = @@IDENTITY

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT ProfileId, Description, Status FROM Profiles WHERE (Description like '%' + @IDescription + '%' or @IDescription = '')

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT Description, Status FROM Profiles WHERE ProfileId = @IProfileId

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: UPDATE Profiles SET Description = @IDescription, Status = @IStatus WHERE ProfileId = @IProfileId

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: DELETE FROM ProfileOptions WHERE ProfileId = @IProfileId

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT ISNULL(D.ProfileId,0) ProfileId, ISNULL(C.OptionId,0) OptionId, CASE WHEN ISNULL(D.OptionId,0) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END FlagActive , C.Title Title, B.Title TitleSubModule, A.Title TitleModule FROM Options C INNER JOIN Options B ON C.IdFather = B.OptionId AND C.Status = 1 INNER JOIN Options A ON B.IdFather = A.OptionId AND A.Status = 1 AND B.Status = 1 LEFT OUTER JOIN ProfileOptions D ON D.OptionId = C.OptionId AND D.ProfileId = @IProfileId WHERE ISNULL(A.IdFather,0) = 0

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: DELETE ProfileUser WHERE ProfileId = @IProfileId AND UserId = @IUserId RETURN 0

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT ISNULL(ProfileId, 0) ProfileId, u.UserId, [User], Name FROM ProfileUser PU RIGHT OUTER JOIN [User] U ON PU.UserId = u.UserId AND PU.ProfileId = @IProfileId WHERE ISNULL(ProfileId, 0) = 0 AND (u.[User] LIKE '%'+@Iuser+ '%' OR @Iuser = '') AND (U.Name LIKE '%' + @IName+'%' or @IName = '') AND U.UserId NOT IN (select OngUserId from OngUser)

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT PU.ProfileId, U.UserId, U.[User], u.Name FROM ProfileUser PU INNER JOIN [User] U ON PU.UserId = U.UserId WHERE PU.ProfileId = @IProfileId

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: UPDATE [User] SET Password = @IPassword WHERE UserId = @IUserId

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT UserId, Type, u.[User], Password, Name, Status FROM [User] u WHERE (u.[User] like '%'+@IUser+'%' or @IUser = '') AND (Name like '%'+@IName+'%' or @IName = '') RETURN 0

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: SELECT u.UserId, u.[User], u.Name, u.Type, u.Status FROM [User] u WHERE u.UserId = @IUserId

Property.Name: HeaderContents
BodyScript
Property.Value: UPDATE [User] SET [User] = @IUser, Name = @IName, Status = @iStatus WHERE UserId = @IUserId
